    "Finally, classical differential expression testing also recovered fewer known driver genes and TFs as our correlation-based analysis (Extended Data Fig. 9f).",
    "Our RealTimeKernel incorporates gene expression changes within and across experimental time points.",
    "Notably, these complementary views allowed identifying a putative progenitor population and substantially more relevant drivers compared to approaches focusing on a single data view.",
